hosts.name: Amellia
hosts.bio: Well I like travelling. I am travelling frequently in the himalayas since 2010. I am a cinematographer, Video editor by profession. I used to be a freelance trekking guide and a photographer in the various parts of the hiamlayan mountain region. Currently living in Jibhi, Himachal pradesh. We can talk about himalayas, it's various ranges, high altitude trekking in the himalayan region, adventure Photography, cinematography, film making etc

hosts.name: Carmela
hosts.bio: Here I am on this adventure! I've always liked sharing my spaces with friends or relatives and so I thought to myself why not make it an activity? I'm originally from a small town near Reggio Calabria but Turin has been my city for 30 years now and I'm really enthusiastic about it. I live with my son Emanuele and my super big cat Whisky. I enjoy cooking and always experimenting with new dishes and it seems that my guests appreciate it a lot. When I can afford it, I love to travel, but I don't disdain a good book or a show and Turin really offers a lot. From the Jazz festival to classical music, to the festival for the very young. I therefore believe that I can satisfy the needs of my guests by offering them friendliness and maximum comfort.

hosts.name: Romain
hosts.bio: Artist and communication/design consultant, I was born and raised in France. I love strolling the streets of Paris, which led me to compile walking tours based on my best urban discoveries.I also love meeting visitors, welcoming them comfortably, guiding them and helping them enjoy the best of Paris.

hosts.name: Doris
hosts.bio: Hi everybody, this is my first time on Airbnb as an host, but in my life I've always loved to meet new people, discover new cultures and share experiences. I love to cook, and as cooking is a form of love it's beautiful when shared. If you come to my place I'll be pleased to share our free time together and why not a good meal. I also love to read books, go to museums or art exhibitions, listen to music (techno/house/funky/pop/rock) and to watch TV series, yes I'm kind of addicted to them. I like to go out, to be with my friends, go to parties or dance, but I also like to share a good glass of wine or a well made gin tonic ;) If you want to find out more about me come to my place and just ask! :D
